Best Practices for Using the &lt;address&gt; Tag

Use &lt;address&gt; to enclose contact details of the document’s author or owner.
Avoid using &lt;address&gt; for unrelated contact information.
Place &lt;address&gt; within relevant sections, like [[footer|]] to associate contact info appropriately.

HTML &lt;a&gt; Tag
The &lt;a&gt; tag defines a hyperlink, which is used to link from one page to another. The most important attribute of the &lt;a&gt; element is the href attribute, which indicates the link’s destination. This attribute determines where the user is directed upon clicking the link.
Syntax:
&lt;a href = &quot;link&quot;&gt; Link Name &lt;/a&gt;
By default, links appear as follows in all browsers:

Unvisited links: Underlined and blue.
Visited links: Underlined and purple.
Active links: Underlined and red.

Example:
&lt;a href=&quot;jenna-personal-website.netlify.app/&quot;&gt;My website&lt;/a&gt;
Opening links in new tab
&lt;a href=&quot;jenna-personal-website.netlify.app/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;My website&lt;/a&gt;
Linking to Email Address
&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:example@gmail.com:&quot;&gt;Send email&lt;/a&gt;
Creating Internal Page Anchor
&lt;a href=&quot;#home&quot;&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;
Example:
&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt;
    &lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;My First Page&lt;/title&gt;

    &lt;style&gt;
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: green;
        }
        abbr{
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1 rem;
            border-bottom: 1 px dashed #007bff;
        }
        abbr:hover{
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #0056b3;
        }

        address {
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }

    &lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;Welcome to my First Page&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;address&gt;
        Author Name: Jenna | Address: Port Louis, Mauritius
    &lt;/address&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;
        A place where you will learn 
        &lt;abbr title=&quot;HyperText Markup Language&quot;&gt;HTML&lt;/abbr&gt; 
        and 
        &lt;abbr title=&quot;Cascading Style Sheets&quot;&gt;CSS&lt;/abbr&gt; 
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;(This will open on the same tab)&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;
        Visit my website: 
        &lt;a href=&quot;jenna-personal-website.netlify.app/&quot;&gt;Visit&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;(This will open on the Another tab)&lt;/p&gt;
